<div class="row">
    <div id="check-wcag" class="col-md-4">
        <button class="btn btn-primary rounded mb-2"> Click to TEST WCAG </button>
        <h3>YOUR CUSTOM TEMPLATE HERE</h3>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center"><hr class="m-0 w-100"><div class="mx-2">OR</div><hr class="m-0 w-100"></div>

        <p>If you want to add wcag checking make sure the parent container uses div id="wcag-check"</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="tool-wp-table-tree {{treeclass}}">

